data.description: BACK ON MARKET: Buyer financing fell through.  Welcome home to this beautiful 2 bedroom, 1 full bathroom brick bungalow!  This move-in-ready home features an updated bathroom and new luxury vinyl plank floors throughout the kitchen, living room, and bedroom.  Washer, Dryer, Fridge, Garage Fridge, Oven, Microwave, and Dishwasher included with the home.   Newer water heater.  Fenced in backyard and 3 car garage for plenty of storage.  Whole house generator included.  Close to major express ways and shopping.  Schedule your showing today!  B.A.T.V.A.I.
